    "An entity in the text essentially indicates anything that is regularly mentioned or made reference to.",
    "With the usage of named entity recognition, it is possible to automatically scan the complete articles which is used to recognize the key entities such as locations, people, companies, cities, businesses, addresses, age, geographic locations, phone numbers and other various type of entities that are addressed.",
